# Code Structure

## Main Components

- [main.py](mdc:main.py) - Entry point that initializes the menu and dispatches to task modules

## Utilities
- [utils/menu.py](mdc:utils/menu.py) - Interactive CLI menu with arrow key navigation
- [utils/logger.py](mdc:utils/logger.py) - Logging setup and configuration
- [utils/database.py](mdc:utils/database.py) - SQLite database operations
- [utils/http.py](mdc:utils/http.py) - HTTP client and request handling

## Tasks
- [tasks/registration.py](mdc:tasks/registration.py) - Wallet registration functionality
- [tasks/twitter.py](mdc:tasks/twitter.py) - Twitter account binding
- [tasks/mining.py](mdc:tasks/mining.py) - Scheduled mining job implementation

## Configuration
- [config.py](mdc:config.py) - Default configuration constants
- [settings.yaml](mdc:settings.yaml) - User-configurable overrides

## Data Flow
1. User input files from `data/` directory are processed
2. Task modules access configuration from [config.py](mdc:config.py) and [settings.yaml](mdc:settings.yaml)
3. Account data is stored in [taker.db](mdc:taker.db) SQLite database
4. Task results are written to files in the `results/` directory
